Class ShapeBoundsTest

    • com.jme3.scene.shape.ShapeBoundsTest

  • public class ShapeBoundsTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Tests that all shapes have had a world bound calculated, and that vertices are within those bounds. Test added for issue #1121. This is a clear failure: BoundingBox [Center: (0.0, 0.0, 0.0) xExtent: 0.0 yExtent: 0.0 zExtent: 0.0]
